""Ko e Otua mo Tonga ko hoku tofia""@en

"Tonga, officially the Kingdom of Tonga, is a sovereign state and an archipelago comprising 176 islands scattered over 700,000 square kilometres of the southern Pacific Ocean. Fifty-two of these islands are inhabited. Lengthwise, the Kingdom stretches over a distance of about 800 kilometres in a north-south line located about a third of the distance from New Zealand to Hawaii."@en
